{"tid":1469361,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[癱瘓．整合] 今日去旅行，但我寧願大家拖得冧機場","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:13:03.000Z","uid":4512,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4100e6344a563dccd5dfafca6d308abff8dd53","tid":1469361,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:01.000Z","msg":"好耐之前已經安排左去旅行，唔係去好長途，但都叫畀晒錢安排晒行程。呢兩個月發生嘅事都搞到我其實好冇心情，個個禮拜都出去發夢、救火<br />\n<br />\n我星期一有去拖冧機場，尋晚要執行李冇去到，睇到直播真係覺得好心酸，我覺得大家好有決心，但真係要諗個好啲嘅方式<br />\n<br />\n好多巴絲提出過應該點做先至可以令到成個行動持續到之餘，又最安全、保障到各位手足，我貼番啲link俾大家睇，唔再重複<br />\n<br />\n我想強調，與其100% 阻機場一兩日然後無以為繼，我地更加需要以星期計既行動。好多熟航空業既巴絲都提出過，就算你只係減慢左佢30%、50%, 個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">雪球效應</span></span>都會影響到之後幾日，冇咁快消化到，而我地要既係size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">滾雪球</span>[/size=6]<br />\n<br />\nQuote 返自己喺第二個post 講既：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>唔夠人寧願等第二日<br />\n<br />\n我明你地想人少都繼續整停機場，但主動封路係將自己放入不利之地，又比人指責、又有風險<br />\n<br />\n人多停佢100%, 人少減慢佢30% 都好過用封路阻旅客去達到100%。總知機場一日唔係100%運作緊，其實就會不斷積累航班，今日又清唔晒上一日既機，已經會有效果<br />\n<br />\n唔夠人的話，我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係要諗個機制大家輪流去，而唔係改變我地既手段</span>。否則個行動做一日就game over, 好快回復正常</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要點做，睇吓下面啲post<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望今晚會見到大家，如果我上唔到機，我拎埋喼同大家一齊行機場！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zaHC9sp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzaHC9sp.jpg&h=36dea74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n<br />\n我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗 (下集)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464134</a><br />\n<br />\n「軍規」唔想今晚機場嘅嘢重演同我入哂嚟!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467593</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70Obur2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70Obur2.jpg&h=df4e4174&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc746d3e25b18d7fc47b18f1cc7223aab55dbbfa","tid":1469361,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7742a07388a683d204dd42289fd6e1dc858144f","tid":1469361,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84aeabfa51ae20a22f13f199c1e3a6c33b0e1a9d","tid":1469361,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bc31c3a2d73a0badd0224dc189c9967aba6c08","tid":1469361,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:37:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23d1ee2ef00d97fc875f4331cf2757e7d8db0cfc","tid":1469361,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:38:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7407551eda78a9f303d59b4a4580106f946bb137","tid":1469361,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23d1ee2ef00d97fc875f4331cf2757e7d8db0cfc","tid":1469361,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:38:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"啱呀，唔好失焦，處理轉就唔好圍幾個鐘..."},{"pid":"d3eed5eab70f4bf033198fe3023cc8a8fa428803","tid":1469361,"uid":4512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:03.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1af99306142e68b66a2379f5d689becd24c93315","tid":1469361,"uid":14370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:04.000Z","msg":"我都係今晚飛 中午打算